  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_004439.wav",
    "text": "你想吃奶奶呀？"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_006435.wav",
    "text": "我刚才不小心打到这儿了。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_002543.wav",
    "text": "完全不可能这么对我的。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_001249.wav",
    "text": "好不好？啊。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_001186.wav",
    "text": "你怎么还在哭啊啊？"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_001843.wav",
    "text": "啊。啊。妍妍舔屁眼舔的舒服吗？"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_005384.wav",
    "text": "内裤到丝袜"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_003909.wav",
    "text": "不行了，我得先睡一会儿了。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_005340.wav",
    "text": "瑞特别持久。光前戏。就能玩小梅一个多小时呢？"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_000773.wav",
    "text": "到时候。咱们的孩子喝不完。多余的奶水就给老公喝。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_002466.wav",
    "text": "我没有换太奶子勾引你们。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_001861.wav",
    "text": "妍妍喜欢在公共场合玩，咱们可以去楼道里。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_002512.wav",
    "text": "我的小穴里真的好烫。慢一点。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_006212.wav",
    "text": "好了好了啊。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_000377.wav",
    "text": "小天，我刚才说的局长。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_005368.wav",
    "text": "我不能丢下你走。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_005732.wav",
    "text": "感觉就要高潮，哦。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_005155.wav",
    "text": "润滑油凉凉的。龟头大大的。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_001084.wav",
    "text": "嗯。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_004587.wav",
    "text": "杰克。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_002323.wav",
    "text": "啊，哦哦。哦。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_005743.wav",
    "text": "我都感觉到人家的淫水啊。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_003858.wav",
    "text": "贾大人。贾大人把你的精华"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_001339.wav",
    "text": "啊，你射的我一脸。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_000424.wav",
    "text": "我要忍不住叫出来了。好哼。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_003980.wav",
    "text": "您就给小女子讲一讲嘛。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_003546.wav",
    "text": "哎，要我用奶子给你按摩。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_005946.wav",
    "text": "啊，我的小穴真的好舒服。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_004019.wav",
    "text": "小女子真的好想要啊。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_004928.wav",
    "text": "啊，这鸡巴的味道。啊。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_001007.wav",
    "text": "啊，全身都被爸爸的大鸡巴操软了。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_002074.wav",
    "text": "顶的姐姐好舒服嗯。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_005371.wav",
    "text": "喝奶。去凉裤，我的奶。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_005177.wav",
    "text": "不？女王要加快了。挺住啊。哎呦，再低一点，屁股撅的高一点。哦，对。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_000946.wav",
    "text": "你饶了儿媳吧。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_004352.wav",
    "text": "蛋蛋。这么晚了，别打游戏了吧。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_002484.wav",
    "text": "好爽啊。感觉好刺激。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_002699.wav",
    "text": "用力贴在一起。把儿子的大鸡巴像这样。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_004326.wav",
    "text": "你满脸都是。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_000901.wav",
    "text": "啊。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_001824.wav",
    "text": "嗯。嗯。嗯。嗯。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_005326.wav",
    "text": "但是我没有开口的话，西西可不能射出来啊？小梅这一个月。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_000662.wav",
    "text": "背着你。就那种事呢。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_000041.wav",
    "text": "就这样。揉大了一点。把我的奶子从胸罩里面推出来。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_005477.wav",
    "text": "三。二。一。"
  },
  {
    "audio_path": "segments/segment_002065.wav",
    "text": "急死我了。"
  }
]